				<td colspan="2"><span>I have to agree with Scambon.  Epic 1.5 and 2.0 are intended to be items of &quot;epic proportions&quot; (pun only partly intended).  They should represent serious effort.  It is premature to judge how &quot;hard&quot; the epics will be until we start to see the new strength of level 66 - 70 groups.  
<br />

<br />
I recall when POP first came out and I started trying to do the POJ trials.  Everyone in my groups were below 65.  Very few people I grouped with had planar gear.  We did not have many of our songs/spells.  AND we were still learning effect techniques.   Last week I took an ALT to POJ to do some trials and it was simple.
<br />

<br />
What takes 3 to 5 groups right now, might very well take 1 to 2 when the impact of Omens is more fully realized. 
<br />

<br />
Do not assume that 1.5 is beyond your grasp until you see the extend of your new reach.
<br />

<br />
Trump
